  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK707">
<l>mukattiṉ mutukkuṟainta tuṇṭō vuvappiṉuṅ</l>
<l>kāyiṉun tāṉmun tuṟum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there anything so full of knowledge as the face ? (No.) it precedes the mind, whether (the latter is) pleased or vexed.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
